{"coredata": {"prism:url": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/article/pii/S0038081418302925", "dc:identifier": "doi:10.1016/j.soin.2018.09.015", "eid": "1-s2.0-S0038081418302925", "prism:doi": "10.1016/j.soin.2018.09.015", "pii": "S0038-0814(18)30292-5", "dc:title": "Des robots affectifs et\u00a0sociaux pour le\u00a0soin, enjeux et\u00a0probl\u00e9matiques \u00e9thiques ", "prism:publicationName": "Soins", "prism:aggregationType": "Journal", "prism:issn": "00380814", "prism:volume": "63", "prism:issueIdentifier": "830", "prism:startingPage": "57", "prism:endingPage": "60", "prism:pageRange": "57-60", "prism:number": "830", "dc:format": "application/json", "prism:coverDate": "2018-11-30", "prism:coverDisplayDate": "November 2018", "prism:copyright": "\u00a9 2018 Published by Elsevier Masson SAS.", "prism:publisher": "Published by Elsevier Masson SAS.", "dc:creator": [{"@_fa": "true", "$": "Devillers, Laurence"}], "dc:description": "\n               R\u00e9sum\u00e9\n               \n                  L\u2019arriv\u00e9e des robots dans notre soci\u00e9t\u00e9 suscite souvent des fantasmes et des peurs. Les\u00a0robots affectifs et sociaux ont d\u00e9j\u00e0 de premi\u00e8res applications\u00a0pour le soin. Une r\u00e9flexion \u00e9thique est n\u00e9cessaire\u00a0pour encadrer l\u2019usage de ces objets ayant des capacit\u00e9s de simuler des dialogues, semblant \u00eatre \u00e9motionnels et capables d\u2019apprendre.\n               \n            \n               Summary\n               \n                  The arrival of robots in our society often arouses fantasies and fears. Emotional and social robots are already being used in healthcare. Ethical analysis is necessary to regulate the use of these objects which are able to simulate dialogues, appearing to feel emotions\u00a0and to\u00a0be capable of learning.\n               \n            ", "openaccess": "0", "openaccessArticle": false, "openaccessType": null, "openArchiveArticle": false, "openaccessSponsorName": n